fields.name: Andrea Vitello Live
fields.description: Grammy and Golden Globe Award-winning composer Andrea Vitello returns to the stage for a major new arena tour, joined by a band, orchestra and choir to perform hit compositions as newer material.

fields.name: Marcus Arnold's One Night Stand Up
fields.description: Following the critically acclaimed sold out arena leg of his tour ‘Monster Project’, Marcus Arnold returns with his biggest globe-spanning stand-up tour to date. Riding high on the success of his TV show 'Bish Bash Bosh', and his critically acclaimed Netflix special 'Meerkats', Marcus is back on stage where he belongs, making sense of a world that’s spinning out of control.

fields.name: The Paranoid Mice World Tour
fields.description: World dominating, multi-award nominated The Paranoid Mice are set to release a highly anticipated EP this Spring. Regarded as one of the world’s greatest live acts, the band will perform in 19 countries including 7 shows in the UK.

fields.name: The Paranoid Mice World Tour
fields.description: World dominating, multi-award nominated The Paranoid Mice are set to release a highly anticipated EP this Spring. Regarded as one of the world’s greatest live acts, the band will perform in 19 countries including 7 shows in the UK.

fields.name: BCM Awards
fields.description: The annual BCM awards returns for the 25th year to celebrate the biggest acts in Blues and Country Music.

fields.name: Scooby: On the Road Again
fields.description: Comedy wonder Scooby with his highly anticipated brand-new stand up show – Two Faced – on Friday 12 February 2021. This will be Scooby’s eighth stand up show and it is shaping up to be his best yet.  It will see him performing across the UK, Ireland, America, Canada and Europe. He can’t wait to be back on the road again!!

fields.name: Young Pretenders
fields.description: BRIT and Grammy-nominated quintet, Young Pretenders kick off their biggest world tour to date.

fields.name: Legends: Garcia vs Doyle
fields.description: Unified Heavyweight Champion of the World Charly Garcia will defend his WBO and IBO World Titles against modern legend Brennan Doyle

fields.name: Eva
fields.description: Global pop superstar Eva has announced  'Madam on A Mission' tour which will see her perform songs from her brand new upcoming album 'Madam on a Mission', due for release January 20th

fields.name: Ice Hockey Championship
fields.description: The 80th event hosted by the International Ice Hockey Association determines champions of the year and division placements for 2022
